==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Pursuer
<hw>Pur*su"er</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>One who
pursues or chases; one who follows in haste, with a view to
overtake.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <fld>(Eccl. & Scots Law)</fld> <def>A plaintiff; a
prosecutor.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Pursuit</ent>⟦br⟧
